	author = {Shiraiwa, S. and Meneghini, O. and Parker, R.R. and Wallace, G. and Wilson, J. and Faust, I. and Lau, C. and Mumgaard, R. and Scott, S. and Wukitch, S. and Beck, W. and Doody, J. and Irby, J. and MacGibbon, P. and Johnson, D. and Kanojia, A. and Koert, P. and Terry, D. and Vieira, R. and {the Alcator C-Mod team}},
